HEADWORD: Denali
<hw>Denali</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The native name for
Mount McKinley in Alaska, translated as <xlati>the great
one</xlati>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Mount McKinley.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def> a national park in Alaska in which Mount McKinley
is located.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Denali national park.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Denarcotize</ent>⟦br⟧
